  "text": "Prior to scaling, we paid attention to the following three points; 1) choice of an appropriate scaling model, 2) protein binding on microsomal incubation, and 3) application of hepatic plasma ‰ow rate. We chose a dispersion model because it is most suitable for high clearance drugs. [CITATION_1] Iwatsubo et al. [CITATION_2] reported that the FH of high clearance drugs would be underestimated by a wellstirred model and overestimated by a parallel-tube model.",
  "correct_citation": {
